---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MGEO | Matías Georgetta - Excelencia Legal y Gestión Deportiva">
  
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-dark via-transparent to-brand-dark"></div>
    
    <div class="absolute -top-[10%] -left-[10%] w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-[10%] -right-[10%] w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/15 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl relative z-10 text-center px-6">
      <div class="mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-6 py-2 backdrop-blur-md">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
        <span class="text-gray-300 font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold">Arquitectura de Resultados</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[11rem] font-heading font-bold leading-none mb-10 tracking-tighter text-white">
        MGEO<span class="text-brand-primary">.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-heading italic font-light text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight mb-12">
        El nexo estratégico entre el <span class="text-white">derecho corporativo</span> y el <span class="text-white">alto rendimiento</span> deportivo.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 pt-6">
        <a href="#unidades" class="group flex items-center gap-4 text-white font-body font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all">
          Explorar Unidades
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:border-brand-primary transition-all duration-500">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" /></svg>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm relative z-10 shadow-[30px_30px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
            <img src="/matias-geo.png" alt="Matías Georgetta" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-light -z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-10 -right-4 w-full h-full border border-brand-primary/10 -z-10"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs mb-6 block">Dirección General</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-8 tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Matías Georgetta<br/>
            <span class="italic font-light text-gray-400 text-3xl md:text-5xl">Visión e Integridad.</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 font-light text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-brand-light pl-8">
            <p>
              Bajo la firma MGEO, hemos consolidado una estructura única que combina el rigor técnico del <span class="text-brand-dark font-medium">Estudio Jurídico</span> con la visión global de nuestra <span class="text-brand-dark font-medium">Agencia Deportiva</span>.
            </p>
            <p>
              Nuestro compromiso es simple: brindar una defensa inquebrantable de los intereses de nuestros clientes, ya sea en el directorio de una empresa o en la mesa de negociación de un club internacional.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-6">
             <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-sm">
                <p class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-primary font-bold mb-1">Licencia Oficial</p>
                <p class="font-heading font-bold text-lg">FIFA ID 202305-1916</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="unidades" class="py-24 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-4">Unidades Operativas</h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-px bg-brand-primary mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        
        <a href="/estudio" class="group relative aspect-video md:aspect-[4/5] bg-[#1a1a1a] overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-primary/30 transition-all duration-700">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505664194779-8beaceb93744?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
           <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-dark via-brand-dark/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-brand-dark/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
           
           <div class="relative z-20">
             <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] mb-4 block">Áreas Civiles y Corporativas</span>
             <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">MGEO Abogados</h3>
             <p class="text-gray-400 font-light text-sm max-w-xs mb-8 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
               Especialistas en ART, Accidentes de Tránsito, Sucesiones y Derecho Corporativo.
             </p>
             <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-white font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] border-b border-brand-primary pb-2 group-hover:gap-6 transition-all">
               Ingresar <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
             </span>
           </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/sports" class="group relative aspect-video md:aspect-[4/5] bg-[#1a1a1a] overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-primary/30 transition-all duration-700">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574629810360-7efbbe195018?q=80&w=2036&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
           <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-dark via-brand-dark/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-brand-dark/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
           
           <div class="relative z-20">
             <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] mb-4 block">Gestión Deportiva Elite</span>
             <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">MGEO Sports</h3>
             <p class="text-gray-400 font-light text-sm max-w-xs mb-8 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
               Representación estratégica, intermediación y scouting de futbolistas profesionales.
             </p>
             <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-white font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] border-b border-brand-primary pb-2 group-hover:gap-6 transition-all">
               Ingresar <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
             </span>
           </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>